{"tid":1794043,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"巴西總統:獲美國取消加徵鋼鋁關稅","createTime":"2019-12-23T00:00:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T00:07:43.000Z","uid":141151,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ad059b39a15a8c171038cc99ab8120309b681794","tid":1794043,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T00:00:44.000Z","msg":"巴西總統:獲美國取消加徵鋼鋁關稅<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2335525/%E5%B7%B4%E8%A5%BF%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%3A%E7%8D%B2%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E5%8A%A0%E5%BE%B5%E9%8B%BC%E9%8B%81%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2335525%2F%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%25B5%25B1%253A%25E7%258D%25B2%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%258F%2596%25E6%25B6%2588%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%25BE%25B5%25E9%258B%25BC%25E9%258B%2581%25E9%2597%259C%25E7%25A8%2585&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwRAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=20fce382\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2335525/%E5%B7%B4%E8%A5%BF%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%3A%E7%8D%B2%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E5%8A%A0%E5%BE%B5%E9%8B%BC%E9%8B%81%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85</a><br />\n<br />\n巴西總統博爾索納羅(Jair Bolsonaro)表示，與美國總統特朗普通電，談了15分鐘，並說服了特朗普取消對巴西鋼鋁產品加徵關稅。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在社交媒體帖文指，雙方交談愉快，並就貿易等多個議題作討論，但未有提及關稅安排。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在本月初宣布，恢復對巴西和阿根廷進口鋼鋁加徵關稅，懲罰兩國操控貨幣貶值，損害美國農民利益。"},{"pid":"f0d35c7d710b9d4b338c006299327b4ca9797589","tid":1794043,"uid":293951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T00:01:34.000Z","msg":"聯手打尻中共啦唔撚該"},{"pid":"6e8058a027b76fc2a3394d7671ba89f55a555358","tid":1794043,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0d35c7d710b9d4b338c006299327b4ca9797589","tid":1794043,"uid":293951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T00:01:34.000Z","msg":"聯手打尻中共啦唔撚該"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T00:07:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}